Description: Fits the Penalized Adaptive Weighted Proportional Hazard (PAWPH)
    model for robust survival analysis in the presence of outliers. Uses
    per-observation intercepts and an adaptive lasso penalty to simultaneously
    perform variable selection and outlier detection. Based on the method of
    Luo, Gao, and Halabi (2022, <doi:10.1002/sim.9424>). Incorporates a modified
    Cox regularisation routine adapted from the ncvreg package
    (Breheny and Huang, 2011, <doi:10.1214/10-AOAS388>).
